        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve" xml:lang="grc">
                <ab>
                 <lb n="1"/>Οὐδεὶς 
                 <lb n="2"/><choice><orig>ά</orig><reg>ἄ</reg></choice>ξιος τ<choice><orig>ω</orig><reg>ῶ</reg></choice>ν 
                 <lb n="3"/>σηνδε
                 <lb n="4" break="no"/>δεμέ
                 <lb n="5" break="no"/>νων τα<choice><orig>ι</orig><reg>ῖ</reg></choice>ς 
                 <lb n="5"/>σαρκυ
                 </ab>
            </div>
            <div type="apparatus">
               <p>Pending</p>
            </div>
            <div type="translation">
                <p>No one of those who are tied to carnal (desires and pleasures is worthy to approach, draw near, or serve You, glorious King).

</p>
            </div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Good condition. The words συνδεδεμένων and σαρκικαῖς are misspelled.  The inscription is from the Prayer of the Cherubic Hymn.
</p>
            </div>
